Quick Overview

A light that shines through history's midnight, to eternity's dawn.God has always been concerned that man should have adequate warning of events to happen in the future.Revelation contains these warnings - a set of prophecies spanning human history from beginning to end.This vital book describes itself as 'the Revelation of Jesus Christ,' and He is certainly its central figure. Not only does it picture Him as revealing what is to come, but it shows that He will come personally - as the only hope for a world in chaos. 




 

